# Groq

> Ultra-fast LLM inference powered by custom LPU (Language Processing Unit) hardware. Free tier with generous limits, ideal for automation and real-time applications.

---

## Overview

Groq provides the fastest publicly available LLM inference:
- **~500 tokens/second** output speed (vs ~50 for typical providers)
- **Free tier** with 14,400 requests/day
- **Llama, Mixtral, Gemma** models available
- **OpenAI-compatible API** for easy migration

### Why Groq?

| Feature | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Speed** | 10x faster than alternatives |
| **Cost** | Free tier: 14,400 req/day |
| **Models** | Llama 3.1, Mixtral, Gemma 2 |
| **API** | OpenAI-compatible |
| **Reliability** | 99.9% uptime SLA |

